'''肩胛骨間棕色脂肪組織'''（{{lang|en|'''I'''nterscapular '''B'''rown '''A'''dipose '''T'''issue}}，簡稱'''IBAT'''）<ref>{{cite journal
 |url     = http://ceps.com.tw/ec/ecjnlarticleView.aspx?jnlcattype=2&jnlptype=10&jnltype=718&jnliid=941&issueiid=8113&atliid=96407
 |title   = 肩胛骨間棕色脂肪組織於大白鼠適應低溫環境時之生理角色
 |author  = 沈友直;廖斐瑩;陳介甫;王家儀
 |journal = The Chinese Journal of Physiology
 |volume  = 34
 |issue   = 4
 |year    = 1991
 |pages   = 427-437
}}{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，俗稱'''冬眠腺'''（Hibernating gland）<ref>{{cite journal
|author   = Elroy F. Sheldon
|title    = The so-called hibernating gland in mammals: A form of adipose tissue
|journal  = The Anatomical Record
|volume   = 28
|number   = 5
|pages    = 331-347
|year     = 1924
|url      = http://dx.doi.org/10.1002/ar.1090280502
|doi      = 10.1002/ar.1090280502
|publisher= Department of Histology and Embryology, Stimson Hall, Cornell University, Ithaca, New York
}}</ref>。它其實並不是一種[[腺體|腺體]]<ref>{{cite web
 |1           = 
 |url         = http://www.vivo.colostate.edu/hbooks/pathphys/misc_topics/brownfat.html
 |title       = Brown Adipose Tissue
 |title_zh    = 多胞性脂肪細胞
 |date        = 2002-08-08
 |author      = Laura Austgen
 |accessdate  = 2009-02-04
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20100624182712/http://www.vivo.colostate.edu/hbooks/pathphys/misc_topics/brownfat.html
 |archivedate = 2010-06-24
}}</ref>，而是生物學家對於一種位於[[動物|動物]]的頭、頸到[[肩胛|肩胛]]之間的部位，主要以[[多胞性脂肪細胞|多胞性脂肪細胞]]為組成部份的[[淋巴腺|淋巴腺]]組織<ref>{{cite journal
|author  = Nnodim, J. O. 與 Lever, J. D.
|journal = Anatomy and Embryology
|title   = The pre- and postnatal development and ageing of interscapular brown adipose tissue in the rat
|volume  = 173
|issue   = 2
|pages   = 215-223
|year    = 1985
|date    = 1985-12-01
|url     = http://dx.doi.org/10.1007/BF00316302
|doi     = 10.1007/BF00316302
|publisher= Springer Berlin / Heidelberg
}}</ref>的一種俗稱。這個組織是一種[[原始脂肪組織|原始脂肪組織]]（primitive fat organs）<ref>{{cite book
|author=Wassermann, F.
|year=1965
|title=Handbook of Physiology, Section 5: Adipose Tissue
|editor=Renold, A. E. & Cahill, G. F., Jr., eds.
|pages=87-100
|publisher=American Physiological Society, Washington
}}</ref>，分為左、右兩球<ref name=BrJNutr />，主要用來儲存中、小型脂肪滴及發達的細胞小器官，以方便身體透過代謝過程而把脂肪轉化成為能量。

冬眠腺只在[[囓齒類|囓齒類]]及[[食蟻類|食蟻類]]動物出現，但其他動物及人類亦存有近似的組織，但只在胎兒期出現。
生物學家在1970年代後期發現IBAT在[[囓齒類|囓齒類]]動物能夠調節體重及身體的核心溫度，若把實驗鼠的IBAT切除，會令實驗鼠的體重增加<ref name=BrJNutr>{{cite journal|
|author=E. CONNOLLY, R. D. MORRISEYT AND J. A. CARNIE
|journal=The British Journal of Nutrition
|year=1982
|volume=47
|pages=653-658
|title=The effect of interscapular brown adipose tissue removal on body-weight and cold response in the mouse
}}</ref>。

